You work at a company that works with projects. 
You develop the software to track all the projects. 
You need to keep(save) the initial budget valor. 
When the project reaches 0 in money you need to remove it
from the company's list of active projects and put it in disabled projects.

You also need to add to the project the employees
and their positions total salary for the duration of the project.
{project : name, total_budget : float ,  current_budget
get : float, employees {name: string , salary: float , position:  }, }